<head /> 
<div3 type="ad-blank" n="1" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="646" />  </p> </div3> </div2> 
<div2 type="notices" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<div3 type="orders" n="1" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head type="nobreak">Richmond Encampment K. T., <num value="2">no. 2</num>--orders <num value="3">no. 3</num>.--</head> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="647" /> --You are hereby summoned to assemble in the <rs type="place">Lodge</rs> Room, (<placeName reg="Bosher's Hall">Bosher's Hall</placeName>,) on <dateStruct full="yes"><day type="name" full="yes">Wednesday</day></dateStruct> <time>Evening</time>, the 19the inst., at half, past <time value="7oclock">7 o'clock</time>. </p> <closer> By order of <signed>the <rs>E. Commander</rs>.</signed> <lb /> <signed><persName n="Dewitt,,T.,H.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00326" reg="default:Dewitt,T.,H.,," authname="dewitt,t.,h."><foreName full="yes">T.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">H.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Dewitt</surname></persName>,</signed> <lb /> mh <num value="18">18</num>--2t <signed><rs type="role" reg="Captain-General">Captain General</rs></signed> </closer> </div3> 
<div3 type="orders" n="2" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head type="nobreak">Masonic notice.</head> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="648" /> --The members of <q direct="unspecified">"<placeName reg="Richmond Randolph Lodge">Richmond Randolph Lodge</placeName>, <num value="19">No. 19</num>,"</q> are requested to meet at a stated meeting of said <persName n="Lodge,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00327" reg="mostcommon:Lodge,nomatch:0" authname="lodge"><surname full="yes">Lodge</surname></persName>, at <placeName reg="Marsons' Hall">Marsons' Hall</placeName>, in this city, at <time value="7pm">7 o'clock P. M.</time> This Evening. --Transient brethren in good standing are also requested to attend. </p> <closer> By order of <signed>the <rs>Worshipful Master</rs>:</signed> <lb /> mh <num value="18">18</num>--1t <signed><persName n="Lester,Secretary,John,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00328" reg="default:Lester,John,,," authname="lester,john"><foreName full="yes">John</foreName> <surname full="yes">Lester</surname>, <roleName n="Secretary" full="yes">Sec'y.</roleName></persName></signed> </closer> </div3> 
<div3 type="orders" n="3" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head type="nobreak">Daily Union Prayer meeting.</head> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="649" /> --A union Prayer Meeting, under the <orgName n="Young Men's Christian Association" type="association">Young Men's Christian Association</orgName>, chiefly to supplicate the <name>Divine</name> blessing upon our Confederacy, will be held every Evening (except <dateStruct full="yes"><day type="name" full="yes">Sunday</day></dateStruct>) until further notice, at <num value="0.25">a quarter</num> to <time value="5oclock">5 o'clock</time>, in the <orgName n="Methodist Church" type="church">Methodist Church</orgName>, (<persName n="Doggett,Doctor,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00329" reg="mostcommon:Doggett,nomatch:0" authname="doggett"><roleName n="Doctor" full="yes">Dr.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Doggett</surname></persName>'s,) at the corner of <address><street n="Broad Street">Broad</street></address> and <address><street n="10 Street">10th streets</street></address>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="650" /> The pasters and congregations and strangers in the city are invited to attend and participate in the meeting.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="651" />mh <num value="17">17</num>--3t </p> </div3> </div2> 
