<head type="nobreak">Runaway--</head> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="653" /> <measure n="25dollars" type="currency">$25</measure> reward. </p> 
<p> Run away from the subscriber, a negro Boy, named <persName n="Arthur,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00330" reg="mostcommon:Arthur,nomatch:0" authname="arthur"><surname full="yes">Arthur</surname></persName>, about <measure n="15years" type="date">fifteen years</measure> old, very black, with pop eyes, bushy hair, and a scared, furtive look. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="654" /> The above reward will be paid on his apprehension and delivery to me. </p> 
<p>

