<div3 type="orders" n="1" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head type="nobreak">Recruits wanted for an Infirmary Company.</head> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="735" /> --Having obtained from the <rs type="role" reg="Secretary of War">Secretary of War</rs> authority to organize an Infirmary Company, to go into the active service of the <placeName reg="United States" key="tgn,7012149" authname="tgn,7012149">Confederate States</placeName> for the war, I respectfully call upon all persons subject to militia duty to enlist in this new branch of the service.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="736" />This company's duties will be to attend the wounded soldiers on a field of battle, and to prevent them from bleeding to death.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="737" />The company will be stationed a short distance in the rear of the line of battle, to immediately dress the wounds of each soldier wounded and remove him from the field to some proper hospital.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="738" />Each man enlisting will receive the bounty of <measure n="50dollars" type="currency">$50</measure>. Uniforms and equipments also furnished.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="739" />Having nearly my complement of men, I should like to receive about <num value="30">30</num> more good recruits.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="740" />Apply soon at my recruiting office, <address><street n="Broad street">Broad street</street></address>, between <address><street n="6 Street">6th</street></address> and <address><street n="7 Street">7th</street></address> streets. </p> <closer> mh <num value="18">18</num>--8t* <signed><persName n="Herbig,,John,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00361" reg="default:Herbig,John,,," authname="herbig,john"><foreName full="yes">John</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Herbig</surname></persName>.</signed> </closer> </div3> 
<div3 type="orders" n="2" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head><orgName type="mil" key="MDBattalion">Maryland Battalion</orgName>.</head> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="741" /> The undersigned has been authorized to organize a Battalion of Infantry, to form part of the <placeName key="tgn,7007516" n="1.000 9" reg="maryland" authname="tgn,7007516">Maryland</placeName> Line. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="742" /> Under an act of Congress, approved <date value="1862-02-15" authname="1862-02-15">February 15, 1862,</date> any native or adopted citizen of <placeName reg="Maryland" key="tgn,7007516" authname="tgn,7007516">Maryland</placeName> may, upon his own application, be transferred at once to the <placeName key="tgn,7007516" n="1.000 9" reg="maryland" authname="tgn,7007516">Maryland</placeName> Line.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="743" />Or any company composed of citizens of <placeName reg="Maryland" key="tgn,7007516" authname="tgn,7007516">Maryland</placeName> or the <orgName n="Columbia District" type="district">District of Columbia</orgName> may, upon application, be so transferred. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="744" /> Individuals or companies desirous of joining this Battalion, will apply in person at the <orgName>office of Weston</orgName> &amp; <persName n="Williams,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00362" reg="nearbymention:Williams,Philip,,," authname="williams,philip"><surname full="yes">Williams</surname></persName>, <address><street n="Pearl Street 15">No. 15 Pearl street</street></address>, or by mail to </p> <closer> <signed><persName n="Weston,,J.,A.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00363" reg="default:Weston,J.,A.,," authname="weston,j.,a."><foreName full="yes">J.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">A.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Weston</surname></persName>.</signed> <lb /> mh <num value="18">18</num>--ts <placeName reg="Richmond, Richmond, Virginia" key="tgn,7013964" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond, Va.</placeName> </closer> </div3> 
<div3 type="orders" n="3" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>Attention<lb /><orgName n="Battery"><persName n="Sturdivant,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00364" reg="mostcommon:Sturdivant,N.,A.,,:1" authname="sturdivant,n.,a."><surname full="yes">Sturdivant</surname></persName>'s Battery</orgName>.</head> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="745" /> We can still accept <num value="25">twenty-five</num> Recruits.--Apply at <hi rend="smallcaps"><orgName><persName n="Darracott,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00365" reg="mostcommon:Darracott,Charles,R.,,:1" authname="darracott,charles,r."><surname full="yes">Darracott</surname></persName>, <persName n="Harts,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00366" reg="mostcommon:Harts,nomatch:0" authname="harts"><surname full="yes">Harts</surname></persName> &amp; Co.</orgName>'s,</hi> <address><street n="Main Street 112">No. 112 Main street</street></address>, or the <name>Rendezvous</name>, corner of <address><street n="Bank Street">Bank</street></address> and <address><street n="11 Street">11th streets</street></address>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="746" /> Members who have not reported will do so at once. </p> <closer> <signed><persName n="Sturdivant,,N.,A.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00367" reg="default:Sturdivant,N.,A.,," authname="sturdivant,n.,a."><foreName full="yes">N.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">A.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Sturdivant</surname></persName>,</signed> <lb /> <signed><persName n="Hewitt,,T.,M.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00368" reg="default:Hewitt,T.,M.,," authname="hewitt,t.,m."><foreName full="yes">T.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">M.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Hewitt</surname></persName>,</signed> <lb /> <signed><persName n="Weisiger,,W.,H.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00369" reg="default:Weisiger,W.,H.,," authname="weisiger,w.,h."><foreName full="yes">W.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">H.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Weisiger</surname></persName>,</signed> <lb /> mh <num value="18">18</num>--5t* <signed><persName n="Darracott,,Charles,R.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00370" reg="default:Darracott,Charles,R.,," authname="darracott,charles,r."><foreName n="Charles" full="yes">Chas.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">R.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Darracott</surname></persName>.</signed> </closer> </div3> 
<div3 type="orders" n="4" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> <opener> <dateline> <name type="place">Hdq'rs Crutchfield <orgName type="mil" key="LightArtillery">Light Artillery</orgName>,</name> <date value="1862-03-13" authname="1862-03-13">March 13th, 1862.</date> </dateline> </opener> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="747" />Attention, Volunteers! </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="748" /> Battery Housed. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="749" /> The undersigned, having secured a splendid Battery of field-places, have authority to raise a company of <orgName type="mil" key="LightArtillery">Light Artillery</orgName>, to be mustered in the <orgName n="Provisional Army" type="misc">Provisional Army of <placeName reg="Virginia, United States, North and Central America" key="tgn,7007919" authname="tgn,7007919">Virginia</placeName></orgName> for the war, and have received authority from the <rs>Governor</rs> to recruit volunteers from the militia, to fill the ranks of the <name>Crutchfield</name> <orgName type="mil" key="LightArtillery">Light Artillery</orgName>.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="750" />The company will be mustered in as soon as a sufficient number of volunteers have been received.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="751" />A fine opportunity now presents itself to those who do not wish to go as militiamen, to enroll themselves as volunteers.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="752" />No substitutes received. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="753" /> Apply at the office of the <orgName n="Old Dominion Insurance Company" type="company">Old Dominion Insurance Company</orgName> under the <rs type="place">St. Charles Hotel</rs>. </p> <closer> <signed><persName n="Crutchfield,,Stapleton,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00371" reg="default:Crutchfield,Stapleton,,," authname="crutchfield,stapleton"><foreName full="yes">Stapleton</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Crutchfield</surname></persName>,</signed> <lb /> <signed><persName n="Wortham,,Charles,E.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00372" reg="default:Wortham,Charles,E.,," authname="wortham,charles,e."><foreName n="Charles" full="yes">Chas.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">E.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Wortham</surname></persName>.</signed> <lb /> mh <num value="13">13</num>--ts(if) </closer> </div3> </div2> 
