<milestone unit="sentence" n="854" /> To rendezvous at <placeName reg="Monterey, Highland, Virginia" key="tgn,2113061" authname="tgn,2113061">Monterey, in Highland county</placeName>, and to report their presence there, for orders, to <persName n="Johnson,General,Edward,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00408" reg="default:Johnson,Edward,,," authname="johnson,edward"><roleName n="General" full="yes">General</roleName> <foreName full="yes">Edward</foreName> <surname full="yes">Johnson</surname></persName>, who is at <placeName reg="Camp Alleghany">Camp Alleghany</placeName>, <placeName reg="Highland, Virginia, Virginia" key="tgn,2002168" authname="tgn,2002168">Highland county</placeName>: </p> <cit><q rend="break" direct="unspecified"> 
