<milestone unit="sentence" n="855" /> The forces of the counties of <placeName reg="Highland, Virginia, United States" key="tgn,2002168" authname="tgn,2002168">Highland</placeName>, <placeName key="tgn,7014398" n="1.000 2" reg="pendleton, west virginia, united states" authname="tgn,7014398">Pendleton</placeName>, and <placeName key="tgn,2002287" n="1.000 3" reg="pocahontas, west virginia, united states" authname="tgn,2002287">Pocahontas</placeName>. </p> </q></cit> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="856" /> To rendezvous at the <rs>New Fair Ground</rs>, near <placeName key="tgn,7013964" n="1.000 11" reg="richmond, richmond, virginia" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond</placeName>, and to report to <persName n="Winder,General,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00409" reg="nearbymention:Winder,Jonathan,H.,," authname="winder,jonathan,h."><roleName n="General" full="yes">General</roleName> <surname full="yes">Winder</surname></persName>: </p> <cit><q rend="break" direct="unspecified"> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="857" /> The forces of the county of <placeName reg="Henrico, Virginia" key="tgn,1002467" authname="tgn,1002467">Henrico</placeName>, and the city of <placeName key="tgn,7013964" n="1.000 11" reg="richmond, richmond, virginia" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond</placeName>. </p> </q></cit> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="858" /> The <rs>Enquirer</rs>, Whig.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="859" />and Dispatch, publish daily for <num value="1">one</num> week, and all the country papers in the <rs>State</rs> will publish this proclamation <num value="3">three</num> times mh <num value="10">10</num>--1w </p> </div4> </div3> </div2> 
