<milestone unit="sentence" n="892" /> --Sealed proposals will be received at this office until <time value="12mid">12 o'clock M.</time>, <date value="1862-03-25" authname="1862-03-25">March 25th, 1862,</date> for the delivery at <placeName key="tgn,7013964" n="1.000 11" reg="richmond, richmond, virginia" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond</placeName> of </p> 
<list type="simple"> 
<head /> 
<item>400 Hospital Tents, 14x15 feet, <measure n="11feet" type="distance">11 feet</measure> high, <num value="4.5">4½</num> foot wall, complete, with flies, poles and pins.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="893" /></item> 
