<item><num value="1000">1,000</num> Wall Tents, 9x9, <num value="4">4</num> foot wall, complete, with flies, poles and pins.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="895" /></item> </list> 
<p> Bids may be made for any number of tents over <num value="1000">one thousand</num>.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="896" />Specimen tents, to which contractors must conform, can be seen at this office.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="897" />Bidders will state the time required to furnish the whole of their bids.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="898" />Payments will be made on delivery of each <num value="500">500</num> tents, and the right to pay <num value="1">one</num>-<num value="4" type="ordinal">fourth</num> in Confederate bonds is reserved.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="899" />Bids to be sealed, enclosed, and endorsed <q direct="unspecified">"Proposals for Tents."</q> </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="900" /> Bids are also invited for manufacture of such Cloth as the <rs>Government</rs> can procure into Hospital, <persName n="Bell,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00416" reg="nearbymention:Bell,George,,," authname="bell,george"><surname full="yes">Bell</surname></persName>, and Wall Tents — the contractor to furnish poles, pins, rope, &amp;c., and to give satisfactory security for performance of contract.

