<milestone unit="sentence" n="902" />Bids to be sealed, and endorsed <q direct="unspecified">"Proposals for manufacturing Tents."</q> </p> <closer> By order <rs type="role" reg="Quartermaster-General">Quartermaster General</rs> C. S. A. <lb /> <signed><persName n="McCLELLAND,,J.,B.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00417" reg="default:McCLELLAND,J.,B.,," authname="mcclelland,j.,b."><foreName full="yes">J.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">B.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">McCLELLAND</surname></persName>,</signed> <lb /> mh <num value="8">8</num>--t25mh <signed><rs type="role2">Major</rs> and A. Q. M.</signed> </closer> </div3> </div2> 
