<head type="nobreak">Attention Military</head> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="909" /> --We can supply you with gray Military Overcoats, lined with good warm lining, and trimmed with eagle buttons, gray Coats, Jackets and Pants, properly trimmed for infantry and artillery service <unclear>los</unclear> Rubber Cloth, for Blankets, Woolen,. Cotton Flannel, and <rs n="cotton socks" type="product">Cotton Socks</rs>; Handkerchiefs, suspender, &amp;c, all of which we offer at very moderate prices. </p> <closer> <signed><persName n="Baldwin,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00418" reg="mostcommon:Baldwin,nomatch:0" authname="baldwin"><surname full="yes">Baldwin</surname></persName> &amp; <persName n="Williams,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00419" reg="nearbymention:Williams,Philip,,," authname="williams,philip"><surname full="yes">Williams</surname></persName>,</signed> <lb /> mh <num value="12">12</num> <num value="116">116</num> and <address><street n="Main Street 118">118 Main street</street></address>. </closer> </div3> </div2> 
